Description: dual AviSynth+ and VapourSynth logo removal plugin
 DelogoHD removes or re-applies logos stored in .lgd logo files. The plugin
 supports planar YUV 4:2:0, 4:2:2, and 4:4:4 clips with 8, 10, 12, 14, or
 16-bit integer samples.
 .
 This package installs one dualsynth plugin binary and exposes it through both
 AviSynth+ and VapourSynth plugin directories.
